# Create phi+ = (|00> + |11>)/sqrt(2)
    phi_plus = QuantumCircuit(2)
    phi_plus.h(0)
    phi_plus.cx(0, 1)
    phi_plus.measure_all()

    # Create phi- = (|00> - |11>)/sqrt(2)
    phi_minus = QuantumCircuit(2)
    phi_minus.h(0)
    phi_minus.z(0)
    phi_minus.cx(0, 1)
    phi_minus.measure_all()

    # Run using Sampler with AerSimulator
    backend = AerSimulator()
    sampler = Sampler(mode=backend)
    job = sampler.run([phi_plus, phi_minus], shots=1024)
    result = job.result()

    counts_plus = result[0].data.meas.get_counts()
    counts_minus = result[1].data.meas.get_counts()

    fig = plot_histogram(
        [counts_plus, counts_minus],
        legend=["Φ+", "Φ-"],
        title="Bell States"
    )
    return fig
